Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,0)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年11月1日 第1層·起始之鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是 夠鬧騰的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是這樣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結衣身體沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.26,0:00:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧昨晚好好休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.37,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才能這麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也有過這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子在22層的森林裡迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像失憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在起始之鎮…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想可能會有人知道關於這孩子的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你有什麼頭緒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 我想這孩子以前並不住在起始之鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.43,0:01:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲開始的時候 孩子們或多或少都留下了心理創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有辦法不理這些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才開始在這間教堂裡照料他們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都會在鎮上巡視 看看有沒有遇到麻煩的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從來沒有見過長得像結衣的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫尤莉耶爾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.16,0:01:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是軍方人士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.58,0:01:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了昨天的事而來抗議的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 哪裡的話 正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是前來道謝的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我過來是有事拜託兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託？

Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:59.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}認めてた臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:07.77,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}分からないままに怖がってた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}後ろの自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:16.72,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:21.83,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}ここはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:29.37,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}儚い心 乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:35.08,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}夢で高く飛んだ躰は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.94,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}どんな不安纏っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:39.98,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:44.42,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}眠る小さな想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.64,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}気づく 弱い 私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:55.40,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}君がいれば 暗い世界 強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:03:01.16,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}長い夢見る心は そう 永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.27,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:10.87,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:59.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}正視著膽怯的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:07.77,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}依然無法理解地畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}背後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:16.72,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}此刻映照在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:21.83,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}描繪了數片天空的此處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:23.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}一定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:29.37,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}亂我脆弱心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:35.08,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}乘著夢想高飛身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:37.94,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}無論有任何不安糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:39.98,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}都掙脫前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:44.42,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}將沉睡著的小小的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.64,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}擴展開來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}意識到弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:55.40,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}只要有你在 黑暗的世界 也能一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:03:01.16,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}用沉眠許久的心 永遠堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:05.27,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:10.87,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

